               <msContents>
                  <summary>On the Unity and Trinity of God. F<locus target="#1r">fols. 1r, </locus>-14r: First sermon on God's three-fold existence, ድርሳን ቀዳማይ በእንተ ፍካሬ ፫ ህላዌሁ.  F<locus target="#14r">14r, </locus>-39v: Second sermon on God becoming Man, ድርሳን ቀዳማይ በእንተ ከሢተ ትስብእቱ ለወልድ. F<locus target="#39v">39v, </locus>-51v: Third sermon on the Interpretation of the Old Testament, ድርሳን ሣልሳይ በእንተ ትርጓሜ ብዙኀ ነገር እምአሪት. F<locus target="#51v">51v, </locus>-62r: Fourth sermon on the Interpretation of Passover and the Lamb of God, ድርሳን ራብዕ በእንተ ከሲተ ትርጓሚ ፍሥሕ. F<locus target="#62r">62r, </locus>-77r: Fifth sermon Explaining Spiritual Warfare, ድርሳን ኃምሰ በእንተ ከሚተ ፀብእ ዘየፀብአዎሙ.  F<locus target="#77r">77r, </locus>-85v: Sixth sermon Explaining Honor of Sunday, ድርሳን ሳድስ በእንተ ከሲተ ክብሩ በዕለተ እኁድ. F<locus target="#85v">85v, </locus>-93r: Seventh sermon Explaining the Practice of Fasting on Wednesday and Friday, ድርሳን ፯ በእንተ ከሲተ ምክንደተ ጾም.  F<locus target="#93r">93r, </locus>-101r: Eighth sermon Explaining about the Practice of Fasting, ድርሳን ሳምን በእንተ ከሲተ ጾም ምንት ውእቱ እፎ. F<locus target="#101r">101r, </locus>-110v: Ninth sermon Explaining the Victory of Christ's Crucifixion over Death, ድርሳን ታስዕ በእንተ ከሢተ ውእቱ ሞት ዘሞአ. 110v-121r: Tenth sermon Explaining Patience in True Faith, ድርሳን ዓሥር በእንተ ከሲተ ጽንዓ ሃይማኖት ርትዕት. F<locus target="#121r">121r, </locus>-137v: Eleventh sermon on the Interpretation of the Praises of Moses and Miriam, ድርሳን ፲ወ፩ በእንተ ትርጓሚ ስብሐት ሙሴ ወማርያም. F<locus target="#137v">137v</locus>-143r: Twelfth sermon on the Confession of Believers and their Patience in Adversity, ድርሳን ፲ወ፪ በእንተ ኑዛዜ መሃይምናን. </summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
